## Interactivity

Interactivity can be added to the graph with the following steps.

First, the dataui package must be loaded.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
remotes::install_github("timelyportfolio/dataui")
library(dataui)
```
:::


### Interactive Sparklines

The code below prepares the list field for the sparkline


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
report <- report %>%
  group_by(Product) %>%
  summarize(`Monthly Sales` = list(Sales))
```
:::


A sparkline can be created with the code below. The resulting graph has features such as:

-   Points and labels

-   Reference lines

-   Bandlines


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code  code-fold="true" code-summary="Show code"}
reactable(
  report,
  defaultPageSize = 13,
  columns = list(
    Product = colDef(maxWidth = 200),
    `Monthly Sales` = colDef(
      cell = react_sparkline(
        report,
        highlight_points = highlight_points(
          min = "red", max = "blue"),
        line_width = 1,
        bandline = "innerquartiles",
        bandline_color = "green"
        )
    )
  )
)
```

